title: No backlight on MacBook Air 2015 820-00165
message:
Working on a MacBook Air 2015 820-00165 that had minor liquid damage.  It's not displaying any backlight.  The machine fully boots and does display an image.

On Q7706 I'm seeing:
PIN 4 - 8.5V
PIN 3 - 8.5V that switches to 3V while booting
PIN 1,2,5,6 - 8.5V 

Suggestions ?

​​​​​​​

title: No backlight on MacBook Air 2015 820-00165
message: Voltage on pin 3-4 and 18-19 from J8300???

title: No backlight on MacBook Air 2015 820-00165
message:
J8300 has:
PIN 3 - 8.5v
PIN 4 - 8.5v
PIN 18 - 3.29v
PIN 19 - 3.29v
